FBIS4-2828 "drchi072_i_94004" FBIS-CHI-94-072 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 East Europe Delegation Publicizes Heilongjiang in Czech Republic Delegation Publicizes Heilongjiang in Czech Republic SK1304021594 Harbin Heilongjiang People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2200 GMT 12 Apr 94 SK1304021594 Harbin Heilongjiang People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [Text] On 12 April at the Small Town Square, the meeting hall of the Czech Republic's chamber of commerce, the Heilongjiang people's government delegation held a news briefing to introduce to the people of all circles in Prague the situation of Heilongjiang as well as the fifth Harbin trade symposium that will soon be held. Wang Zongzhang, vice governor of the provincial government and head of the delegation, introduced Heilongjiang and the Harbin trade symposium and invited the businessmen and the personages enterprise circles to participate in the Harbin trade symposium which will be held this June. He ensured that the symposium would provide quality service for the guests from Czech and offer the greatest convenience for trade talks and cooperation.
